reviewText: I enjoyed the extras on going grocery shopping, stocking your kitchen and on visiting a fitness trainer. He teaches you how to cook in real time in a real kitchen. The reciepes are simple and fast.

There are very few videos you could find on Low Carb cooking. I use to watch George on the Food Network channel. He's not theatrical or over zealous with promoting his video. If you are not into it you will find it hard to stay engaged.
